Shoreward Revenant banishment
-1 3 1 1 70 80 3539 7000 6 3500000 0
5819
The Shoreward Revenant, a dead Assessor who administered the jurisdictional boundary at the Shoreward Threshold during the Iseth Reach's final season, has refused to acknowledge the end of its commission. It now blocks legitimate transit to Mafdet and kills any traveler who fails its archaic certification review. The Mafdet postmaster has exhausted conventional responses and requires the Revenant's permanent banishment before the eastern Reach approach can be reopened.
The Shoreward Revenant has been banished and the Shoreward Threshold is open to legitimate transit. Mafdet Warden patrols have conducted a full crossing of the jurisdictional boundary for the first time in recent memory without fatality. The postmaster has issued a formal notice that the eastern Reach approach is now operational and that the ancient assessor commission has been dissolved.

